Description: A comprehensive, AI-powered statistical analysis platform
    delivered as an interactive Shiny application. Dr.AIStat provides
    15 analysis modules covering descriptive statistics, measurement
    analysis (EFA/CFA), group comparison tests, regression, machine
    learning classification, clustering, Item Response Theory (IRT),
    endogeneity tests, advanced Bayesian methods, Structural Equation
    Modelling (SEM/PLS-SEM), Conditional Mediation (CoMe),
    bibliometric analysis, fuzzy-set Qualitative Comparative Analysis
    (fsQCA), STATA-style panel/survival methods, and an AI Research
    Assistant powered by the free Groq API. Launch the app with
    run_draiststat().
